          Your digital garage for your vehicles.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
          Keep track of key dates such as MOT, Insurance, Tax or Warranties. This is a collection of tools for your vehicle, for you to use.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center mt-10 gap-x-6">
          <%= if @current_user do %>
            <a
